{"tid":489702,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[生物學］人類應一夫多妻？","createTime":"2017-12-05T02:47:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-05T11:26:01.000Z","uid":46587,"like":12,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"dc5694900e16ba1705eef07af112865fcc2ce115","tid":489702,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:47:11.000Z","msg":"一個男人可以搞大無限個女人嘅肚（前提係佢有能力）<br />\n但女人被人搞大肚要等10個月<br />\n根本唔需要咁多毒撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然話就話因為文明推進（男女平等？）先發展到一夫一妻<br />\n但係咪一夫多妻先最合乎人類生理構造<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：小學常識科拎90/100"},{"pid":"579d7e74bde6f07f802688d802c36ac221798380","tid":489702,"uid":4085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:50:40.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"7ac8e55a08a9b169def1b39671d56b4efc81fc67","tid":489702,"uid":123713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:53:55.000Z","msg":"岩啊"},{"pid":"bf60230065d22785e47ca3fd15becde7312920bc","tid":489702,"uid":41689,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T02:54:09.000Z","msg":"人口過剩 <br />\n生咁撚多件邊個養<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7740dc06794fddaac16260cc574d1c533bc77cda","tid":489702,"uid":67407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:05:15.000Z","msg":"若果人類生存最終目的只有繁殖既話，係"},{"pid":"d9026a56d501d55508f2b435c205cc0078ff5d31","tid":489702,"uid":88933,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T03:09:25.000Z","msg":"一夫多妻實情係保護緊你呢啲毒撚<br />\n<br />\n你諗下 有錢佬又娶幾十件 靚仔姑爺仔又娶幾十件 <br />\n<br />\n到時娶欣宜就有你份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec125925acb3702966391c2d6046f4fdabbbef1b","tid":489702,"uid":57418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T07:59:49.000Z","msg":"如果加入埋&quot;下一代成長環境&quot;呢個因素又點睇，人類同好多一夫一妻制動物(如鳥類)一樣，主要都係靠雄性作為主要家庭經濟收入來源，一夫多妻係某程度來講係多個家庭（母子）分攤同一經濟來源（父親收入），所以係一夫一妻制下既小朋友既成長環境係好d，所以個人認為除左d好撚有能力既男人之外(有錢同有時間陪伴+教育下一代)，正常人行一夫一妻制(加埋少生子女)係更加適合現代社會環境"},{"pid":"0dc44a8f37ea30c7228c6f7d1debef7469e56f07","tid":489702,"uid":19908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T08:02:57.000Z","msg":"但係啲社會性動物係一妻多夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a741f7f0ea3ab74f63e27515d795fca52d9021b","tid":489702,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:15:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係啲社會性動物係一妻多夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cc18af559372fafc83cf34cfc8912fec362b904","tid":489702,"uid":124899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:18:06.000Z","msg":"只適合一夫多sp"},{"pid":"e90e415055ded70db800051cb035acbdc27bd0ab","tid":489702,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:26:15.000Z","msg":"你講緊結婚同大肚 兩樣都無直接關係"},{"pid":"fc6435cddeec030cfcd5a820a51463607456f9de","tid":489702,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:28:29.000Z","msg":"你諗下好啦<br />\n過多廿幾年你大個仔就會明<br />\n老婆一個真係夠哂架啦 ...."},{"pid":"1f9d09ee31c9551b4bf1d90914d3d60b5bb90a59","tid":489702,"uid":61653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T10:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>但係啲社會性動物係一妻多夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n螞蟻"},{"pid":"0a1cfd78e76d18db3a562845c355f92dcca8b54d","tid":489702,"uid":57418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T11:26:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>但係啲社會性動物係一妻多夫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可唔可以講多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji